classification.comments: Study Data: Built from the 1987 GLTD Basic Tables (See SOA Table Identities 1478 and 1481). Methodology: A margin was added to the Basic Tables. The margin was introduced by decreasing the termination rates (death and recovery combined) to 90 percent of the GLTD Basic Table rates at all durations. Data Transcription Errors Detected: 03/2013. Data Corrected and Certified: 03/2014.
